reviews.review_text:
Someday everything's going to be different Flight from Sweden took forever
Dead were lackluster at the Ice Palace
I was lackluster at the Ice Palace
In Amsterdam a punk threatened to cut my face
if I didn't by his blow.
I forked over some coin
and told him to keep the blow.
almost cut me anyway
until i started yelling Thief! Thief!
Saw some crazy windmills and tulips 
somewhere in Dutch country.
When the train pulled into Germany
The German Military boarded 
with Sub Machine guns
In East Berlin the squatters kept Molotov cocktails on the roof just in case they were attacked again by skin heads.
I feel in love twice, out of love once
Dropped five feet off the Zenith in Paris
and spent the rest of the tour 
including Halloween in crutches
I got just about stripped searched
coming into JFK
even though I was in a wheelchair
I was supremely confident
and almost stupidly cocky
until i got in the cab and remembered
i had traded for a sheet
and it was 
ON MY PERSON.
Thank you Jesus
"Does God look down on the boys
in the barroom "
